result.adr_address: 1 Kornhill Rd, Kornhill, Hong Kong
result.name: KYO Watami

reviews.text: A nice place to gather with friends
Breakfast is available. Very comfortable and quiet in the morning.
Service can be slow at times, offers seasonal menu with items from appetizers, skewers, hotpot, sushi and alcohol.
Set dinners are a good deal. You pick an appetizer, an entre, a drink and a dessert. Comes with salmon sashimi and a Caesar salad. The clams hot-pot is good, sashimi and ramen is only average.
Good value of money Japanese casual restaurant.  Dish in small portion, but you have more selection of dishes
